_:N35b06f86de724527b89a92902ebbb6d7 <http://schema.org/description> "National Museums Liverpool (NML) is a diverse group of museums and galleries. Its collections are among the most important and varied in Europe, and contain everything from Impressionist paintings and rare beetles to a lifejacket from the Titanic and artefacts from ancient Egypt. NML is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ." .
